  &lt;strong&gt;Step 2 - Probability of having cancer if two tests are positive:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
  Positive Predictive Value (PPV): &lt;strong&gt;${(results1.ppv || 0).toFixed(3)}&lt;/strong&gt;
